**Analysis:**

The text contains 128 words and 116 sentences. It uses 143 unique words.

**LIX calculation:**

LIX = (average sentence length / number of words in the text) + (number of unique words / number of words in the text) * 100

LIX = (116/128) + (143/128) * 100
LIX = 90.63 + 111.72
LIX = 202.35

**Result:**

LIX=202.35